{"tid":274761,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"伯賴啲片好唔好睇？","createTime":"2017-06-07T14:14:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-22T15:48:21.000Z","uid":107294,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"59f4f3654a6ae69907b5fc27c1c2436dccfbb806","tid":274761,"uid":107294,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T14:14:46.000Z","msg":"樓主覺得伯賴啲片好高質 <br />\n笑點有水準 配音都好好 自己扮埋女人聲 一腳踢<br />\n角色人物 動畫都做得好好<br />\n可以短短時間表達出一個故事 生動有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 其實我淨係鍾意睇黑伯喜劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔明點解佢唔多出名 少人撐<br />\n連登都好少提起過佢 <br />\n各位巴絲留底個負皮個時 順便講下點解佢唔好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好睇覺得好笑  正皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好睇垃圾   負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31ca9397adaa907d6f27f88fc8bee363f0b6c9e7","tid":274761,"uid":107294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T14:19:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0715a4d5f00502a4c1ae687d2be3a68164cff6b9","tid":274761,"uid":107294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T14:24:08.000Z","msg":"真係好少人識佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33e65aef5c6ffa380df8de398b57a2066904983f","tid":274761,"uid":20899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T14:30:01.000Z","msg":"把聲幾好聽"},{"pid":"625d1795bcce1763a40267d5d142cbdf77591f65","tid":274761,"uid":107294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T14:30:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>把聲幾好聽</blockquote><br />\n留個正評呀ching<img src=\"/assets/faces